"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/76424","Home Office","false","2014-07-22","<p> </p><p> </p><p>We have made a commitment to ban the testing of household products on animals. <br>Although superficially straightforward, the details are not been easy to <br>resolve. Any solution has to be legally viable since we cannot ban testing <br>which may be required under UK or EU law. <br><br>The key issue is around ingredients. I am looking to develop a solution that is <br>workable, but does not have a chain of unforeseen circumstances. It is my <br>intention to implement a ban before the next general election in May 2015.</p><p> </p><p> </p><p> </p>","Lewes","Norman Baker",,"2014-07-22T10:19:13.5057231Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/76424/answer","Biography information for Norman Baker","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/76424/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/76424/answer",,,,,"1","Home Office","Home Office","2014-07-08","Animal Experiments","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for the Home Department, what plans she has to bring forward legislative proposals to ban the testing of household products on animals.","false","Biography information for Andrew Rosindell","Romford","Andrew Rosindell","204393"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/76425","Ministry of Justice","false","2014-07-14","<p>The Government believes the posting of revenge porn is a despicable act and is one which can have devastating consequences for the victim.</p><p> </p><p>The Government is looking seriously at this area of the law to ensure it is strong enough to deal with this behaviour.</p><p> </p><p>I am happy to consider any representations that the National Union of Students wishes to submit.</p><p> </p>","Ashford","Damian Green",,"2014-07-14T13:13:48.1207286Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/76425/answer","Biography information for Damian Green","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/76425/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/76425/answer",,,,,"54","Justice","Justice","2014-07-08","Pornography: Internet","1","House of Commons","To ask the Secretary of State for Justice, what steps the Government is taking to address the problem of revenge pornography; and if he will meet representatives of the National Union of Students to discuss that matter.","false","Biography information for Andy Sawford","Corby","Andy Sawford","204400"
