"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/65976","Cabinet Office","false","2014-07-10","<p>This information could only be provided at disproportionate cost. Details of all Ministerial overseas travel is published on a quarterly basis.</p><p>Information about the Prime Minister and Deputy Prime Minister's visits within the UK are published quarterly.</p><p> </p>","Horsham","Mr Francis Maude","204308","2014-07-10T16:05:59.3828187Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/65976/answer","Biography information for Lord Maude of Horsham","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/65976/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/65976/answer",,,,,"53","Cabinet Office","Cabinet Office","2014-07-07","Domestic Visits","1","House of Commons","To ask the Minister for the Cabinet Office, pursuant to the Answer of 17 June 2014, Official Report, column 506W, on official visits, what domestic visits each of the Ministers of his Department has made since January 2013; and what the purpose of each such visit was.","false","Biography information for Sheila Gilmore","Edinburgh East","Sheila Gilmore","204377"
"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/65977","Cabinet Office","false","2014-07-10","<p>The Prime Minister's Office forms part of the Cabinet Office. In common with other departments, the Cabinet Office pays fees to the Treasury Solicitor's Department for legal advice on a range of issues. The proportion of those fees which relates to the Freedom of Information Act 2000 is not recorded.</p><p> </p>","Horsham","Mr Francis Maude","204270","2014-07-10T16:17:01.6465141Z","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/65977/answer","Biography information for Lord Maude of Horsham","http://data.parliament.uk/resources/65977/answer",,,,,"http://data.parliament.uk/resources/65977/answer",,,,,"53","Cabinet Office","Cabinet Office","2014-07-07","Freedom of Information","1","House of Commons","To ask the Minister for the Cabinet Office, how much the Prime Minister's Office spent on legal fees in cases relating to the release of information requested under the Freedom of Information Act 2000 in each of the last five years.","false","Biography information for John Woodcock","Barrow and Furness","John Woodcock","204306"
